Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:23.42,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}前に進むの 見ていてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:28.15,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}So repeatedly, we won't regret to them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:32.98,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな風にも考えていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.50,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}「憧れ」「抜錨」「未来」
